menu "Bootloader test options"

config BOOTLOADER_TEST_CRC_FORCE_FAIL
    bool "Force app CRC check to fail (validation testing only)"
    default n
    help
        When enabled, the observed CRC is XOR-inverted before comparison,
        guaranteeing a mismatch regardless of image content.
        Use this to verify that BL_EVT:APP_CRC_FAIL fires and the boot
        path enters recovery hold without handoff.
        Must be disabled for all production and public release builds.

endmenu
